Jan 31 (Reuters) - Brazilian tech firm Totvs (TOTS3.SA) said on Monday its Dimensa SA unit had bought financial app developer Mobile2you for 26.9 million reais ($5.07 million). Totvus said in a securities filing that the purchase was aimed at expanding its offer of products and services to its customers and strengthening its position in the B2B technologies segment for the financial sector and fintechs. ($1 = 5.3041 reais) Our Standards: The Thomson Reuters Trust Principles.